name: Patterned Cushion
description:
This cushiony friend of mine is a favourite. 
Abstract, stretchy fabric, mismatched buttons, and a big fat squishy centre… it’s everything a cushion should aspire to be. And so much more.

name: Vinyl Cake Stand
description:
Baking, for some bizarre and unknown reason to myself, seems to be incredibly popular right now.

And It is the cupcake fad that has inspired the creation of my vinyl cake stand…

Although I’m not a fan of cakes, I’m a big fan of these functional, retro cake shelves.

And let’s face it, no one has a use for those Tammy Wynette records anymore.

Made with authentic and working vinyl, complete with silver effect fixings.

Records may vary.

name: Vinyl Clock
description:
This Vinyl Clock is made from authentic and working vinyl. 
 
In a former life I imagine this Transvision Vamp record was loved for what it was.

And it still is. Kind of.

With the addition of a battery operated clock mechanic, this record has taken on a new and improved sound.

Goodbye ‘I Want Your Love’. Hello ‘Tick Tock’

Because you can never have too many, this clock boasts three golden hands (hours, minutes and seconds) and comes complete with hanging device.

name: Knitted Cat
description:
Hand knitted cat looking for a new home.
This beautifully crafted kitty is made from quality black yarn, It has two glass bead eyes that are fixed into position, and a nose that has been stitched with pink cotton. Around the neck is a decorative ribbon with a small bell attached.
